MUST TRYs 
- Pizza dosa: you are a pizza lover or not...you will love this flavor of dosa. It has a cheese filling with chopped capsicum, carrots, onions and tomatoes. Definitely was a  mouth melting  one for me. 
- Tawa idly: I have tried tawa idly at many places, but this is one of my favorites. The flavor of the chutney powder used is very different and delicious. 
The chutneys and sambar were also very good, especially the peanut chutney.
